description:
Invicta Women's Baby Lupah Quartz Five-Piece Leather Strap Watch Set

Choices: Gold-tone Rose-tone or Silver-tone case

The choice is yours with this alluring Invicta Baby Lupah timepiece that includes five leather straps! This set combines the beauty of an Invicta women's timepiece with five gorgeously designed straps. Crafted in a rounded rectangular shape the stainless steel case graces your wrist in your choice of a gold-tone rose-tone or silver-tone. Glossy and gorgeous the case features a polished finish while the bezel boasts a meticulous satin brushed finish.

Peer through the domed sapphire-coated crystal and you'll find an elegant white mother-of-pearl dial. Highly polished case coordinating Arabic numerals are displayed at each hour position. A Swiss Parts Quartz movement maintains time as case matching hour and minute hands exhibit Tritnite luminous filling.

Five genuine leather straps accompany this Baby Lupah and set it apart. In black brown ivory pink and green the straps feature a crocodile-like embossed pattern and come with quick change pins and polished case matching buckles. The straps taper to 14mm and fit a wrist up to approximately 8.

It's a woman's prerogative to change her mind. With this timepiece and strap set there's never a wrong choice!

Complete the look with the matching strap set J401184 J401903 or J402418.

  • Strap: Leather
  • Movement: Swiss Parts Quartz
  • Crystal: Sapphire coated mineral
  • Crown: Push/pull
  • Clasp: Buckle
  • Strap Measurements: 8-3/4 L x 16mm W
  • Case Measurements: 41mm L x 22mm W
  • Water Resistance: 3 ATM - 30m - 100ft

    Gold-tone: 13834
    Rose-tone: 13835
    Silver-tone: 5168
